{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "“大水坑”", "storyInfo": "“大水坑”拆除在即，眾人在這裡最後玩了個痛快。杜林人們期待著下一個地標的誕生，依娜姆也與嘉維爾討論著阿卡胡拉的未來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g2_fountainlake", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據大家表決的結果，陪伴了我們半年多的“大水坑”即將完成它的歷史使命。它會被爆破拆解，重新回歸為工程材料。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市民們，這場稍微延長了一點的夏日狂歡恐怕即將結束了。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚嗚，我會永遠記得這段美好的時光。", "name": "杜林人"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "超級旋轉大滑梯真是怎麼玩都玩不夠，居然就要和它告別了......", "name": "杜林人"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過！取代“大水坑”的，會是更新的，更美的，更不一樣的建築！！畢竟這裡可是際崖城，是最棒的建築設計師們締造的城市！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇·畫布和卡奇·敘光是際崖城新生代裡最引人矚目的建築設計師，他們會在未來的幾個月裡交出自己的設計方案......", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，又會是一場怎樣的強者對決呢！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼呼，簡直讓人想起幾年前，他們初露鋒芒的時候，圍繞著穹頂的那場競標大賽！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年的穹頂之爭沒有勝利者，那麼這次，誰會取得下一個際崖城地標的設計權呢？讓我們——", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先喝口水。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "ypos": 20.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playmusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克羅綺，你今天這個狀態，不會是喝了酒來的吧？", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫時沒有。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這風格可不像你啊。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依娜姆給我看的錄影裡，地上的比賽中有一個職位叫做主持人。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打算拓展一下職業路徑。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之！建築設計師們的設計雖然暫時還等不來，但是，市民們，這個夏天的尾巴可是稍縱即逝！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就讓我們在滑梯消失前的最後時間裡，去玩它個爽吧！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwdcheerup", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦！！！！！", "name": "杜林人"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "enter": "right", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "channel": "run"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "run"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "power": 60.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "times": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "exit", "direction": "left", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "channel": "run"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "run"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特米米，小心！你慢點！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "power": 60.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "times": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "exit", "direction": "left", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前你們在阿卡胡拉的大瀑布玩水，我聽說了以後可是羡慕了好久呢！", "name": "特米米"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，這次我也可以加入啦！", "name": "特米米"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這孩子。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？平常你都小心翼翼地藏著尾巴，這麼一看，是不是又變粗了點？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？才沒有！我來之前才剛用卷尺量過！已經好幾個月沒有變粗了！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，看來真的很在意？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚嗚，看我的潑水攻擊！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#3$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_shuihua", "layer": 1.0, "x": 100.0, "rox": 50.0, "roy": 80.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jump_water", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "ypos": 150.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 80.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很大膽嘛！來就來！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 她們似乎比你更像杜林人呢，斯第奇。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也未必知道什麼叫“杜林人”，魯珀。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你好像有點緊張，在擔心和卡奇的競標嗎？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擔心他？笑話！我還沒淪落到擔心比不過卡奇的境地。不過是他的方案一向比較招外行人的喜歡罷了。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也有些人是比較看好我的方案的，或許我該拿出點不同的風格，好贏過那傢伙。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然乾脆......唉！現在還是別想了！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......說實話，如果不論美學，僅從可玩度上而言，這“大水坑”也還算湊合吧。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 原來你也會享受這些？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偶爾的話。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，你在這啊！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想不想感受下流速全開滑梯的威力？因為會對設備有損耗，平常可沒這機會。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛和極境哥試了幾次，那種速度感！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過掉進水裡的時候會有點疼，你要不要試試？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用，我對這種玩法可沒有一點興趣......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲吼，小心！", "name": "極境"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 1300.0, "ypos": 500.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_shuihua", "x": 200.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jump_water", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 卡奇老弟，這衝擊力，沒的說！水花居然能濺這麼高！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#14$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要不試試換種玩法，比如說......比誰的水花小？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 壓水花？好思路！聽起來不會那麼疼了！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的沙堡......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （卡奇老弟，我們是不是惹禍了。）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（呃，就算是斯第奇，也不至於為了沙堡生氣吧？）", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （可他看起來就是生氣了。）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（要不然我們......）", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "exit", "direction": "right", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "exit", "direction": "right", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slip"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這麼跑了？你們兩個，給我回來！！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "exit", "direction": "right", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，情緒調動相當不錯。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這都是我學習的成果，感謝這些錄影帶。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我們可以用一系列的比賽，維持住“競賽”這個概念的熱潮，再借著幾個月後卡奇和斯第奇的競標，把氣氛推到最高點。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是不是可以印發一批小紙片，讓觀眾們可以借此表達自己對某一方的支持，最後如果猜對了會有點獎品之類的。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們管這東西叫獎券，克羅綺你真是無師自通。地上的商人們可是把這東西當做自己斂財的手段呢。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜林人對這樣賺錢可沒興趣......不如讓輸的那一方承包勝利者一個月的酒吧！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，刺激一點承包兩個月也行。這個可以由投票決定。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後關於輸幾個月酒的競猜或許也能再發一批獎券......", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我開始擔心際崖城市民的未來了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，這種其實沒派上什麼用場的感覺真是難得。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼？你一定得揍些什麼才滿意？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不是。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，如果順利的話，阿卡胡拉能收獲些杜林的技術，這就不算白回來一趟了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾雖然很早就離開了家，但其實還蠻關心阿卡胡拉的吧！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，就算看過了各種各樣的地方，還是雨林裡最讓我安心。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你會回來嗎？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫時還沒這個打算。我在羅德島上還有病人呢。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相當多提亞卡烏希望你回去，你甚至可以考慮成為王酋。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還希望地上會直接長蕉果。這片大地總不會遂了每個人的願。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾，你來擔任阿卡胡拉的王酋是最合適的，只有你才能鎮住所有提亞卡烏。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都在期待著你的回歸。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而如果你實在不願意，那麼，最後結果可能會變成薩爾貢宮廷派一個王酋來管理阿卡胡拉。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，阿卡胡拉一定不會再像如今這麼自由。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依娜姆，不是還有你這個大酋長嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，有些事情我是沒辦法做的。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以想辦法幫大家從外面倒一點破爛回來。但真正能夠把提亞卡烏緊緊擰成一條藤蔓的，不會是我。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依娜姆，我也並不是在逃避責任。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我還沒想好怎麼做。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾居然在“想”，真難得。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，祖瑪瑪，想打架嗎！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的意思是，嘉維爾一般都是做了再去想。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於我自己，或許可以。但如果關於這麼多提亞卡烏......", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該結束的總會結束，不是嗎，就像是這大滑梯一樣，拆掉，然後會建新的。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我剛才沒聽見你們在聊什麼啦，我只是想說，朋友們，趁它還沒消失，我來給你們拍張合照吧。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_summercicada", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "slide"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04", "xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "slide", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，也好，複雜的東西暫時放到一邊。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼下先要盡興！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特米米，你也笑起來！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "x": 400.0, "y": 100.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "xFrom": 400.0, "yFrom": 100.0, "xTo": 350.0, "yTo": 200.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你們已經學會杜林人的哲學了。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟休個假可不容易，怎麼能浪費呢！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得好，我該敬你一杯！想嘗嘗漿果番茄酒嗎？我請。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這個還是算了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "30_i04", "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "imagerotate", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g2_fountainlake", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "用於拆除的炸藥已經佈置完畢，助理機器人也通通做好了準備。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這座帶給了大家無數歡樂的大滑梯即將消失。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但是夏天總要結束，之後一定還會有更濃的快樂。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "每個際崖城的市民都是這麼相信著的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "五、四、三、二、一。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 20.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_run_water", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_water", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "爆炸聲並沒有人們想像的大，大滑梯只是開始緩慢地崩解。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果用一些修辭的話，可以說是溶化在了水中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g3_fountainlake_ruins", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，消失得很輕盈。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#3$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你會喝得爛醉如泥，然後錯過目睹這玩意被炸掉的美好景色。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈哈，我只是比較擅長享受。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但是，在這種時候，我更傾向於保持清醒。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這是我對正在消逝之物最基本的尊重。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#10$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇哦，難道你其實是個深藏不露的聰明人？這種人設就算是在際崖城的圖書館藏書中也算是爛俗了。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你這小子！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#5$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......卡奇。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來就是要動真格的了，我們公平競爭，各憑本事吧。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不介意的話，握個手？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧，出於對另一位際崖城公民最基本的尊重。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "